{"tid":2517520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個俾hall俾人偷嘢經歷/搞笑嘢","createTime":"2021-05-05T11:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T11:44:49.000Z","uid":180960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0fd3f354b798f94e6b532af33900ee39d0ab06a6","tid":2517520,"uid":180960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T11:08:48.000Z","msg":"話說宜家都sem尾，就嚟要退hall，平時有煮下嘢嘅我有個煮食煲，長期都放係廚房<br />\n話說我噚日烚完蛋，洗好隻煲放係一二邊晾乾（由第一日住已經係咁做，無嘢發生過）<br />\n然後今日，我出廚房用微波爐個陣發現......<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">個煲蓋唔見咗</span></span><br />\n究竟做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大佬 你好偷唔偷 偷個煲蓋？！<br />\n<br />\n好啦 我應該都唔會特登去揾返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反正都就走人加上個煲仲係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家又有冇咩想分享嘅宿舍經歷呢？"},{"pid":"560f561237adac14192d89559c132d3f97580f81","tid":2517520,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T11:13:46.000Z","msg":"roommate喺我出咗去個時帶條女返嚟偷情"},{"pid":"afe4efdc7ae1a407472d2e7ee6747d80e1bce46e","tid":2517520,"uid":180960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"560f561237adac14192d89559c132d3f97580f81","tid":2517520,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T11:13:46.000Z","msg":"roommate喺我出咗去個時帶條女返嚟偷情"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T11:15:34.000Z","msg":"唔係偷你情咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10bca2e5dfde0d053a6fcc1134e8dbba09714d0d","tid":2517520,"uid":134883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T11:18:42.000Z","msg":"偷女同學啲bra同底褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87aa13c22a760b148029e6dd224765eb9ae86cf","tid":2517520,"uid":180960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"10bca2e5dfde0d053a6fcc1134e8dbba09714d0d","tid":2517520,"uid":134883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021